divs: Sighting DetailsWe were looking at a bright light that looked like mars. To the upper right of it somthing started moving at a very fast speed with a bright light. It made us think of UFO's. Then it all the sudden disapeared. After about 2 minutes it reapeared to the right of "mars" and did a 180' under mars and started moving left and while it was going left it apeared with 3 lights in a boomerang .We went and grabbed binoculars but when we got back. It was gone and we didn't see it again..
Summary: Apeared and reapeared once, changed direction.
